title: Michael Kors MK5905 - Bradshaw White/Rose Gold One Size
description: Transparent acetate case with a transparent acetate and gold-tone stainless steel bracelet. Fixed rose gold-tone bezel. Rose crystal pave dial with rose gold-tone hands with alternating Roman numeral and index hour markers. Minute markers around the inner bezel. Dial Type: Analog. Chronograph - three sub-dials displaying: 60 second, 60 minute and 12 hour. Quartz movement. Scratch resistant mineral crystal. Solid case back. Case diameter: 43 mm. Case thickness: 12.5 mm. Round case shape. Band width: 22 mm. Band length: 9.5 inches. Deployment clasp. Water resistant at 50 meters / 165 feet. Functions: chronograph, hour, minute, second. Casual watch style. Michael Kors Bradshaw Chronograph Rose Crystal Pave Dial Transparent Resin and Gold-tone Ladies Watch MK5905.
